Project: Exploring TMDB Dataset for year-over-year patterns for movie genres¶

Looking for patterns on:¶

  • #movie releases have changed over years by genre
  • Popularity of genres have changed over years
  • Budget, Revenue and Profit have changed over years

Table of Contents¶

1. Introduction
2. Data Wrangling
3. Exploratory Data Analysis
4. Conclusions

    tmp2 = df.copy().iloc[[i]]

Filling the 0 values for Revenue, Budget¶

In [211]:
def fill_0_values (df, var):
    ix = df[var] ==0
    new = df.groupby(by = ['release_year', 'genres'])[var].transform('mean')
    df.loc[ix, var]=new[ix]
    return df
In [219]:

df_new = fill_0_values(df_new, var = 'revenue_adj')

4.2 Number of movies by Genre : Year over Year¶

Since we are making heatmap again and again let's put that piece in a function

In [96]:
def plot_heatmap (pvt, fmt, title):
    if fmt == 'float':
        fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize = (20,8))
        ax = sns.heatmap(pvt, annot = True, cmap="YlGnBu")
        plt.title(title);
    if fmt == 'int' :
        fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize = (20,8))
        ax = sns.heatmap(pvt, annot = True, cmap="YlGnBu", fmt ='d')
        plt.title(title);

pvt = tmp.pivot_table(index =  'genres', columns = 'release_year', values = 'budget_adj', fill_value=0)
pvt = pvt/1e+6
#1,000,000

# Create heatmap
plot_heatmap(pvt, fmt = 'float', title = 'Budget in Millions')

Observation

  • Adventure, Action and Fantasy are the most popular genres
  • Sporadically Western movies are high budgeted movies as well

4.7 Genres of top profit making movies¶

df_new5 = df_new5[['release_year', 'genres', 'profit_rank']]

Reading the chart

  • In 2014 Adventure = 5; it means that all the top 5 movies had adventure as genre
  • Adventure and Action dominates the top 5 standings

Conclusions¶

Looking at the results of past 15 years, we observe that

  • Action and Adventure are mostly the top 2 genres of movies that makes most profit
  • Fantasy use to be an important profit making genre but not in recent few years
  • Science Fiction is becoming a significant genre now
  • One of the Family movie also make it big at the box office
  • Drama, Crime and Mystery movies are not making through the top 5 cut
